    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c.Bill0].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [c0]

    WHERE [c0].[BillId] = @__billId_0
) AS [t] ON [c.Bill.BillDetails].[BillId] = [t].[Id0]
